Fuse Fabric is included in [Fuse ESB 5.1](http://fusesource.com/products/enterprise-servicemix/) or later. You can get [Enterprise Support, Mentoring, Training and Tools](http://fusesource.com/enterprise-support/support-offerings/) from [FuseSource](http://fusesource.com/). Please do [get in touch](http://fusesource.com/contact) we'd love to help!

Otherwise you may find the [Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)](faq.html) useful or join the [Community](community.html).

We love feedback of all kinds; whether it's thoughts, ideas, suggestions or bug reports! 

